column5: This vent-hole (hereinafter known as IVH) if lost or stolen will not be replaced or purchase price refunded. Violation of IVH rules will result in expulsion without refund. A copy of IVH rules can be obtained from one or more members wearing tie-dyed Oxford shirts after written requests. Frivolity and silliness are highly recommended for all riders. Flamewars are expressly forbidden. Please consult your counselor magistrate or religious functionary before usage. Comment below if you agree. Tonight's lineup: all reruns. Jimmy Kimmel: Zooey Deschanel Sam Richardson Kodak Black (R 6/16/21)Jimmy Fallon: Dave Grohl Lil Nas X Blake Shelton (R 5/24/21)Stephen Colbert: Dr. Sanjay Gupta Rita Moreno (R 6/15/21)Seth Meyers: Joel Edgerton Edward-Isaac Dovere (R 5/27/21)James Corden: Josh Gad Chloe Moriondo (R 6/23/21) update... Sorry I'm running late... just got home from a baseball game and stopped to have a beer with a pal. Giants lost. Beautiful day though! Some sun some fog.
